      "source": [
        "# Cloudkoffer 2026 - ClickHouse Cluster Dashboard\n",
        "\n",
        "Uebersicht aller Services im ClickHouse-Taxi Showcase."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Cluster Nodes\n",
        "\n",
        "| Node | IP | Rolle |\n",
        "|------|-----|-------|\n",
        "| node0 | 192.168.1.100 | Monitoring, DNS, JupyterLab, Webapp |\n",
        "| node1 | 192.168.1.101 | ClickHouse Server, Keeper |\n",
        "| node2 | 192.168.1.102 | ClickHouse Server, Keeper |\n",
        "| node3 | 192.168.1.103 | ClickHouse Server, Keeper |\n",
        "| node4 | 192.168.1.104 | ClickHouse Server |"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Service URLs\n",
        "\n",
        "### ClickHouse\n",
        "\n",
        "| Service | URL | Beschreibung |\n",
        "|---------|-----|-------------|\n",
        "| **ClickHouse node1** | [http://node1.cloud.local:8123/play](http://node1.cloud.local:8123/play) | SQL Playground |\n",
        "| **ClickHouse node2** | [http://node2.cloud.local:8123/play](http://node2.cloud.local:8123/play) | SQL Playground |\n",
        "| **ClickHouse node3** | [http://node3.cloud.local:8123/play](http://node3.cloud.local:8123/play) | SQL Playground |\n",
